---
// ValueProposition.astro
// Bloque de propuesta de valor + storytelling de marca para la Home
// Sprint 3 micro-batch B
---

<section class="value-section" aria-labelledby="value-title">

  <!-- Narrativa de marca -->
  <div class="brand-story">
    <span class="brand-story__eyebrow">Nuestra Tienda</span>
    <h2 id="value-title" class="brand-story__heading">
      Una tienda pensada para pedir fresco,<br />sin vueltas ni pasos de más
    </h2>
    <!-- <p class="brand-story__body">
      Nuestra Tienda nació para reunir nuestras recetas frescas y productos más pedidos en un solo lugar.
      Entrás, explorás el catálogo, elegís tus favoritos y resolvés la compra con una experiencia clara,
      rápida y pensada para volver cuando quieras.
    </p> -->
    <a href="/tienda" class="brand-story__cta">
      Ver catálogo completo
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
        <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Pilares de valor -->
  <div class="value-pillars" role="list" aria-label="Nuestros valores">
    <article class="pillar" role="listitem">
      <div class="pillar__icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 0 20A10 10 0 0 0 12 2z" />
          <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="pillar__title">Fresco del día</h3>
      <p class="pillar__desc">
        No guardamos stock. Preparamos cada pedido en el momento para que llegues el mismo sabor
        que sale de nuestra cocina.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="pillar" role="listitem">
      <div class="pillar__icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" />
          <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="pillar__title">Receta familiar</h3>
      <p class="pillar__desc">
        La base de nuestra fórmula viene de generaciones. Sin trucos, sin atajos: ingredientes
        reales y la técnica que siempre funcionó.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="pillar" role="listitem">
      <div class="pillar__icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" />
          <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="pillar__title">Sin agregados artificiales</h3>
      <p class="pillar__desc">
        Cero conservantes, cero colorantes, cero relleno. Solo aguacate, lima, cilantro, cebolla,
        jalapeño y sal. Leélo en la etiqueta.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .value-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  /* ── Narrativa de marca ─────────────────────── */
  .brand-story {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .brand-story__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-soft) 92%, transparent);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .brand-story__heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .brand-story__body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .brand-story__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }

  .brand-story__cta:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-strong);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent-strong);
  }

  .brand-story__cta svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .brand-story__cta:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  /* ── Pilares de valor ───────────────────────── */
  .value-pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-elevated) 95%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pillar:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px var(--color-shadow-soft);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .pillar__icon-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface-soft-strong), color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-soft) 78%, transparent));
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .pillar__title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .pillar__desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .value-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .brand-story__heading {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .value-pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
